You'll...
develop and scale RESTful APIs;
you'll use Kinesis and Firebase to power our member notifications;
use Redis to improve performance;
write efficient mySQL queries;
develop and thoroughly test code for the most challenging aspects of the product or its sub-systems;
collaborate with other tech teams and architects.
You’re a great fit for our team because...
you're proficient Java 8 (bonus points for Java 11);
you know how to develop RESTful APIs;
you've worked with Spring or Spring Boot;
you have a solid understanding of relational databases with meaningful MySQL experience;
you have used testing frameworks such as JUnit or testNG;
you're familiar with Redis and its data structures;
you have experience with Google Firebase experience (preferred).
